title: Airmen in C-130J crash identified, memorialized (USAF - United States Air Force)
text: ( Source : USAF - United States Air Force ) BAGRAM AIRFIELD, Afghanistan ( AFNS ) -- The six Airmen assigned to the 455th Air Expeditionary Wing who died Oct. 2 when their C-130J Super Hercules crashed shortly after takeoff from Jalalabad
